AfterOrder
export default function AfterOrder(
props
)

Generates page informing the user as to whether or not their order when through and provides them a map to get to anywhere they may be going.

Parameters
props

An object that has a status property that is the HTTP status code returned by the API server when the order was put through

Returns

<div> tag containing the page
